{/* ========================================== How it work ============================================ */}
HOW IT WORKS

5 features that make LIBERA a game changer in the fixed APY projects

1.reduction of tax:Buy Fee:5% Sell Fee:16%

Unlike other fixed APY projects with a buy fee usually ranging from 13% to 16%. LIBERA buy fee is only 5%. This will encourage users to buy and make bigger volumes and also bring higher buy pressure for LIBERA than other fixed APY projects.

{/* ======================================== choose ======================================= */}
--------WHY CHOOSE LEBERA

Limited supply with Highest Burning Rate

Unlike other rebase tokens which are inflationary and have unlimited supply, LIBERA has a limited supply of 50 millions tokens, of which 18% will be burned at launch, and more will be burned every week based on Libero's 1-4% weekly burning speed. Even more, for every sell 25% of the tokens are burned - the highest burning percentage in the whole market - make LIBERA a hyper deflationary token never seen before.

Earn 4,037.20% $Libero APY inside itself

Just by holding LIBERA in your wallet, you will get 4,037.20% APY of Libero or 1.02% value increase everyday. The number of LIBERA in your wallet does not increase, make no inflation and no price decrease over time, while still yielding a very high amount of Libero inside it. Users can get the Libero inside Libera by unwrap it at any time.

Earn high BUSD passive income

You can stake Libera in LIBERA Bank and earn high APR BUSD rewards from both DEXes and CEXes trading volume, plus high LIBERO rewards. For reference Libero Bank rewards are now 642% APR BUSD - highest on the whole Defi market.

Low buy fee with hourly highest buyer rewards

LIBERA has a low 5% buy fee compare with 13-16% buy fee of other fixed APY project. Every hour a 1% of transaction volume will be automatically rewarded to the biggest buyer during that hour. You can now get high income from LIBERA - the world's first deflationary fixed APY token easily by take advantage of the low fee & the hourly buyer rewards

-----------FAQ'S

Frequently Questions

LIBERA
LIBERA BANK

1/ LIBERA is Limited supply and deflationary token: Unlike LIBERO is inflationary token with unlimited supply, LIBERA has a limited supply of 50 millions tokens, in which 18% will be burned at launch, and more will be burned every week based on Libero's 1-4% weekly burning speed.

2/ LIBERA is the first deflationary token that yields 4,037.20% APY inside itself. Just by holding LIBERA you will get 4,037.20% APY of Libero or 1.02% value increase everyday. So the number of LIBERA in your wallet does not increase, make it no more inflation and no more price decrease over time, while still yielding a very high amount of Libero inside it.
